data.description: Great 3 bdrm 1 1/2 bath townhome in Hunters Crossing.  Eat-in Kitchen with all appliances (approx 3 years old), and bay window for natural light.  Living Room, kitchen and hallway has beautiful vinyl planking floor.  Lots of natural light in the living room.  Rounding out the first floor is a half bath & laundry room w/washer & dryer.  Upstairs three spacious bedrooms, primary has a large walk in closet, two linen closets and full bath with double sink.  Full Unfinished basement, with washer/dryer hookups.  Furnace & AC new. Patio in the back, no backyard neighbors. All Minooka schools.  Channahon Park District.
